      "content": "idk i dont know if i buy that. it feels way too convenient. like, they suddenly hand me a high-level position that gives me access to even more sensitive info just as i'm starting to notice things i shouldn't. it feels less like they trust me and more like they're trying to keep me close so they can see exactly what i know. dont you think there's a pattern there?",
